                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">As we see the
                                      local administration relaxing
                                      lockdown restrictions, we hope
                                      that we start to see things
                                      getting back to normal but for now
                                      we will continue to work from
                                      home.</font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">One small but
                                      significant step that we are
                                      planning is to extend help from
                                      the Tech Team. Those facing system
                                      related issues can contact the
                                      Tech Team via email.</font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">Once your request
                                      is put in, the tech team will
                                      coordinate with you for a meeting
                                      date and time when you can come to
                                      the office and get in-person help
                                      from them. At this time, only
                                      selected locations will be open
                                      and only selected employees will
                                      be allowed into the office on-need
                                      basis. </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">All those who do
                                      go to the office, please maintain
                                      hygiene and follow all precautions
                                      possible. No food or water will be
                                      available (except for the tech
                                      team as they will probably stay
                                      longer). </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">For preventive
                                      measures, the Tech team will only
                                      set up 2-3 meetings a day. Please
                                      be patient while your request is
                                      in queue.</font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">For any other
                                      query, please feel free to contact
                                      your HR buddy.</font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000"><br>
                                    </font></div>
                                  <div><font size="-1" face="Verdana"
                                      color="#000000">----------------------------</font></div>
